FBIS4-23353 "drafr107_c_94018" FBIS-AFR-94-107 Daily Report 2 Jun 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA EU To Grant Preferential Trade Tariffs EU To Grant Preferential Trade Tariffs MB0206162394 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in English 1400 GMT 2 June 94 MB0206162394 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network English BFN [Text] The European Union is to grant preferential trade tariffs to South Africa. This has been announced in Brussels by senior European Commission spokesperson, Pierre Defraigne. He said the concession would be introduced at the beginning of January next year. There is a possibility of the introduction being brought forward.
